org.ngi.zhighcharts
Class ListWrappedIntervalModel

java.lang.Object
  org.zkoss.zul.AbstractChartModel
      org.ngi.zhighcharts.ListWrappedIntervalModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, IntervalModel, org.zkoss.zul.ChartModel
public class ListWrappedIntervalModel
extends org.zkoss.zul.AbstractChartModel
implements IntervalModel

A wrapped interval data model implementation of IntervalModel, which wrap on a ListModelList a list model list of Maps containing data. A XY model is an N series of (X, Y, ) data objects. a client component using this wrapper model this model wrapper listen to source model change events, convert it, and forward it to all client components listening. the mapping between the series and the data to use for it, is defined in a map where the series name is the key, the value contains the key of the data in the map element from list model , you can set some style data in a map for each series

Author:
alain
See Also:
ExtXYModel, Chart, Serialized Form
